      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 64 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 64 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：曳其輪，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject dragging back his (carriage-) wheel. With firmness and correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
