      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 64 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 64 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：未濟，征凶，利涉大川。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject, with (the state of things) not yet remedied, advancing on; which will lead to evil. But there will be advantage in (trying to) cross the great stream.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
