      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 64 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 64 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：貞吉，悔亡，震用伐鬼方，三年有賞于大國。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject by firm correctness obtaining good fortune, so that all occasion for repentance disappears. Let him stir himself up, as if he were invading the Demon region, where for three years rewards will come to him (and his troops) from the great kingdom.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
