      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 64 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 64 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：貞吉，无悔，君子之光，有孚，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject by firm correctness obtaining good fortune, and having no occasion for repentance. (We see in him) the brightness of a superior man, and the possession of sincerity. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
