      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 64 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 64 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：有孚于飲酒，无咎，濡其首，有孚失是。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows its subject full of confidence and therefore feasting (quietly). There will be no error. (If he) cherish this confidence, till he (is like the fox who) gets his head immersed, it will fail of what is right.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
